Add to infra/terraform-github/main.tf:
```hcl
resource "github_repository_environment" "pypi" {
  repository  = var.repository
  environment = "pypi"
  reviewers {
    # Populate with required reviewer team/user ids
  }
  deployment_branch_policy {
    protected_branches     = false
    custom_branch_policies = true
  }
}

resource "github_repository_environment_deployment_policy" "pypi_main_dispatch" {
  repository     = var.repository
  environment    = github_repository_environment.pypi.environment
  branch_pattern = "main"
}
```
This makes the re-key a `terraform apply` (plan-reviewable, state-tracked, drift-detectable) rather than a click.
